{"tid":138352,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"你哋係段關係入面點改變自己？","createTime":"2017-02-28T13:31:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-28T14:24:23.000Z","uid":83863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0c5f551a3018cb4d53fcb24cc9e4fb41ea253562","tid":138352,"uid":83863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T13:31:03.000Z","msg":"逢親對住最close嘅人，例如屋企人同男朋友，我就會好容易好大脾氣，男友話呢個係佢唯一想我改嘅嘢，但年幾都無改善<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都唔知自己係懶去改，定係唔重視呢段關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n相反佢之前ig同fb follow咗好多囡囡，有時人地直播烏低身影住個胸，就喪禁心心，我嘈完幾鑊話唔鍾意，佢之後都unfollow哂，無再咁做。<br />\n<br />\n我個人比較道德撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成日因為佢做嘅嘢發脾氣嘈分手，唔想再係咁，求屌醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15f99c5da156089c12e52a99f2432f5fcc40d0fd","tid":138352,"uid":83941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T13:32:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f210072456cd9678d6632e16df4b263412c57744","tid":138352,"uid":83863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T13:34:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">樓豬一定係ipad</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大波 仲慘<br />\n硬係覺得男友為身材而一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34a08566261523bf0436cd1ee5f21b8e2d1f3879","tid":138352,"uid":21488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T13:34:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">樓豬一定係ipad</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大波 仲慘<br />\n硬係覺得男友為身材而一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfc512d422516beb0395b8d6d75e3