/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10f92c5d6b97b13152fad79d0fb43293a65d7345","tid":138352,"uid":83863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T14:08:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都係 特別係對屋企人 <br />\n明明唔想咁但有時一煩躁上黎就忍唔到 <br />\n之後又好內疚 明明出發點係好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n成日一開口就hurt到人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"120122aace62cca92040fef01d2814ab9e4959aa","tid":138352,"uid":83863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T14:08:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">樓豬一定係ipad</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大波 仲慘<br />\n硬係覺得男友為身材而一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n實係啦 全世界最大波果個 你條仔實鐘意到要生要死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9857af0565f2534213efbdf55ed5e94a91b2d3c9","tid":138352,"uid":70399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T14:09:08.000Z","msg":"做人好難<br />\n都為左好多人改變自己<br />\n但最後都係做反原本既自己<br />\n係夾既一齊玩咪仲開心<br />\n下下去改去就辛苦自己"},{"pid":"ef8dc5693429167ac2aaf72804cfb8f200c5bfa0","tid":138352,"uid":88072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T14:13:05.000Z","msg":"過來人話你知<br />\n郁啲就嘈分手 最後一定係分手收場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n改下啲脾氣 <br />\n你男朋友幾愛你都好 終有一日佢會頂唔順<br />\n唔好令自己後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40af5a144425fd9710494b86c7473f46d5e98815","tid":138352,"uid":3517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T14:14:18.000Z","msg":"我同你差唔多，成日都發脾氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時嬲果陣咪唔